    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>Virtual Currency Tax Reform Act - Directs the Internal Revenue Service (IRS) to treat virtual currencies as a foreign currency for federal tax purposes. Defines "virtual currency" as a digital representation of value that functions as a medium of exchange, a unit of account, and/or a store of value. </p> <p>Imposes a five-year moratorium on any capital gains tax on virtual currencies. </p>]]></text>
